OL,6,FThere is an early-day motion calling
OL,7,Ffor a vote of no confidence, and it
OL,8,Fhas been signed by almost 70 MPs.
OL,10,FBut even Tories and SNP figures admit
OL,11,Fthat it would need more than 200
OL,12,Fsignatories to be a serious threat.
OL,14,F"It's hardly an avalanche," said one
OL,15,Fwhip.
OL,17,FOther MPs have called for colleagues
OL,18,Fto accept Hoyle's apology for his
OL,19,Fmistake and let parliament move on.
