OL,6,FThe level of chaos in parliament
OL,7,Fyesterday over - effectively - the
OL,8,Forder of amendments will seem totally
OL,9,Fbaffling to voters.
OL,11,FAs the Conservative's Leader of the
OL,12,FHouse, Penny Mordaunt, admitted most
OL,13,Fpeople aren't worrying about Standing
OL,14,FOrders, nor discussing the
OL,15,Fparliamentary process over the
OL,16,Fbreakfast table.
OL,18,FBut she argued it was about fairness.
