OL,6,FHowever, threatened with a huge
OL,7,Frebellion (some 100 Labour MPs wanted
OL,8,Fto support the SNP including shadow
OL,9,Fcabinet members)
OL,11,FIn doing so - he caused fury, that
OL,12,Fresulted in the Tories collapsing the
OL,13,Fprocess, Labour's amendment being
OL,14,Fpassed on the nod- and no one voting
OL,15,Fon the SNP's version.
