OL,4,Cchaos despite SNP and Tory fury
OL,6,FTories and Scottish nationalists were
OL,7,Ffurious - and that hadn't dipped this
OL,8,Fmorning. One Conservative MP messaged
OL,9,Fto say - "temperature only going up
OL,10,Fthis morning from what I can see... I
OL,11,Fdon't think he will survive".
OL,13,FWhen I asked another what the anger
OL,14,Flevels were they said - "very high".
OL,15,FAnd WhatsApp's shared between MPs
OL,16,Freiterated that mood.
OL,18,F"He may well be a good man 'overall'
OL,19,Fbut he made a monumental mistake that
OL,20,Fhas ramifications far and wide," said
OL,21,Fone.
