OL,6,F'I don't know if Labour threatened the
OL,7,FSpeaker': SNP Chief Whip Owen Thompson
OL,8,Ftold Anushka Asthana that if any
OL,9,Fattempt to influence Sir Lindsay Hoyle
OL,10,Fwas made it needs 'to be looked at in
OL,11,Fgreat detail'
OL,13,FHoyle apologised to the SNP and
OL,14,Finsisted he'd got it wrong. But he
OL,15,Fexplained his reasoning - around MP
OL,16,Fsafety.
