OL,6,FOther MPs said opposition days were
OL,7,Falways used politically and MPs faced
OL,8,Fabuse over many issues, including for
OL,9,Fvoting against Labour opposition day
OL,10,Fmotions, for example on sewage.
OL,12,FBut they acknowledged that Hoyle was
OL,13,Fobsessed with protecting MPs from
OL,14,Fabuse and said his mistake came from a
OL,15,Fgood place.
OL,17,FMeanwhile aid charities told us that
OL,18,Fpeople in Gaza would be heartbroken to
OL,19,Fsee British MPs focus so much on the
OL,20,Fterminology, when what they believed
OL,21,Fwas necessary was action.
